      <ol class="- topic/ol ">
         <li class="- topic/li ">Competency based training programs must be in place for employees that work in the Hot End and should include; Risk assessments, JHA, procedures and work element sheets/instructions. </li>
         <li class="- topic/li ">All forming employees receive annual machine fire prevention/deluge system and response training.</li>
